display_long_description:
Step into the role of a fearless baboon gifted with gorilla-style locomotion, trapped inside a massive, high-security laboratory deep underground. Once a place of scientific innovation, the facility has fallen into chaos after a catastrophic experiment unleashed unspeakable horrors. The sterile white walls are now stained and cracked, corridors echo with distant metallic groans, and the air hums with the unsettling sound of something moving just out of sight.

Using your powerful arms and unmatched agility, you’ll climb, swing, vault, and leap through shattered walkways, tangled ventilation shafts, and towering research chambers. Every surface is a potential escape route—or a deadly trap. The monsters stalking the halls aren’t mindless; they hunt, adapt, and learn from your every move.

Your only weapons are your speed, your wits, and your ability to master every inch of the environment. Explore abandoned labs, flooded storage bays, and pitch-black maintenance tunnels while piecing together the truth behind the disaster. But be warned: the deeper you go, the more the line blurs between predator and prey.
